BAIRC

An IRC client/bot made in bash. Extremely versatile, but also dangerous. Take care.

> ./bairc irc_server [port]

v0.8

c/ - customizations folder
f/ - important files that BAIRC will use
bairc - main file. execute this
server - server events
actions - irc events
privmsg - PM events ( includes CTCP )
nickname - Nickname that BAIRC will use. Update ./f/nickserv_pw if Nickname is registered with NickServ

